    <item>
      <title>阿根廷贫困率飙升至 50% 以上，紧缩政策带来沉重打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/poverty-soars-past-50-in-argentina-as-milei-austerity-hits-hard</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年上半年，阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱推出休克疗法，试图让本已摇摇欲坠的经济重新站起来，该国的贫困率达到了 2001 年金融危机以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/poverty-soars-past-50-in-argentina-as-milei-austerity-hits-hard</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 19:16:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
